Windows:
 1. Get boost 1.53.0 source tarball & extract
 2. cd boost_1_53_0; bootstrap; b2 toolset=msvc-10.0 link=static runtime-link=shared

Ubuntu:
 1. sudo apt-get install libboost1.48-all-dev 

MacOS X:
 1. Get boost_1_53_0.tar.bz2 & extract
 2. cd boost_1_53_0; ./bootstrap.sh; ./b2 architecture=x86 toolset=darwin threading=multi address-model=32

